  "steps": [
    {
      "id": "tutorial-managing-secrets-01",
      "markerIndex": 0,
      "replayStartSec": 2.418957,
      "replayEndSec": 9.802533,
      "narrationText": "首先，以 env 模式设置一个密钥。该值将作为环境变量注入容器内。首次写入无需任何验证，覆盖已有密钥才需要证明。",
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-managing-secrets/tutorial-managing-secrets-01.c0a4cf03.mp3",
      "textHash": "c0a4cf037c8cac936b31d12ee9342be9a0c558b1887f213b5c1c292ca285cf99",
      "audioDurationSec": 15.56898,
      "afterAudioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-managing-secrets/tutorial-managing-secrets-01-after.393be265.mp3",
      "afterAudioDurationSec": 4.362449,
      "afterTextHash": "393be265572f145eb51e13962fa6d6dab1cb9f71c42209df224e8ec500830e44"
    },
    {
      "id": "tutorial-managing-secrets-02",
      "markerIndex": 1,
      "replayStartSec": 9.802533,
      "replayEndSec": 17.116513,
      "narrationText": "接下来是 file 模式密钥。file 模式不会将值暴露在容器环境变量中，而是通过 Docker 标准机制将其写入 /run/secrets 下的文件。凡是敏感内容，推荐使用此模式。",
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-managing-secrets/tutorial-managing-secrets-02.ac299c21.mp3",
      "textHash": "ac299c21713687e282dc40478bb2497ee1e28f638106ba731ea276074866c56c",
      "audioDurationSec": 14.994286,
      "afterAudioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-managing-secrets/tutorial-managing-secrets-02-after.1173652c.mp3",
      "afterAudioDurationSec": 8.124082,
      "afterTextHash": "1173652cb88c213df420789dea44194746c2fc12cd28e89e4b8eb62eaca33adb"
    },
    {
      "id": "tutorial-managing-secrets-03",
      "markerIndex": 2,
      "replayStartSec": 17.116513,
      "replayEndSec": 21.30037,
      "narrationText": "来列出我们已有的密钥。只显示名称和模式，无论谁在查询，列表都不会显示值。",
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-managing-secrets/tutorial-managing-secrets-03.7927983f.mp3",
      "textHash": "7927983f866021c7b4bce5934fe14ed41fbce3e51bdfc61dfac56ab2d0c623d3",
      "audioDurationSec": 8.359184,
      "afterAudioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-managing-secrets/tutorial-managing-secrets-03-after.197ac871.mp3",
      "afterAudioDurationSec": 4.04898,
      "afterTextHash": "197ac8714a2b59b6d931de4cbe187e2aacce4bff1258de6accf1fa0743a2ac7b"
    },
    {
      "id": "tutorial-managing-secrets-04",
      "markerIndex": 3,
      "replayStartSec": 21.30037,
      "replayEndSec": 26.229426,
      "narrationText": "接下来是让人意外的部分。secret get 命令返回摘要，而不是值本身。没有任何参数能取回明文。这就是 GitHub Actions 的模型：设计上只写不读。",
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-managing-secrets/tutorial-managing-secrets-04.e50ca3c1.mp3",
      "textHash": "e50ca3c131a627b1e0d11c60603c3f42ce202e5e086094074b01380bad4d7324",
      "audioDurationSec": 13.087347,
      "afterAudioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-managing-secrets/tutorial-managing-secrets-04-after.63f384f7.mp3",
      "afterAudioDurationSec": 5.250612,
      "afterTextHash": "63f384f712213f937d6d7b5cc84b19d8d068df3e221bbff46afabedd7b151978"
    },
    {
      "id": "tutorial-managing-secrets-05",
      "markerIndex": 4,
      "replayStartSec": 26.229426,
      "replayEndSec": 36.266224,
      "narrationText": "丢失了值？不要试图查看，而是轮换它。rotate-secret 参数会跳过前置条件检查，审计日志会将此次更改标记为蓄意轮换。公开、有意为之、安全。",
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-managing-secrets/tutorial-managing-secrets-05.8eb6d301.mp3",
      "textHash": "8eb6d3012b5e3416fd5ea46b9b99d40d7dd8742934de4fa0de919610ac2e8ce1",
      "audioDurationSec": 14.915918,
      "afterAudioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-managing-secrets/tutorial-managing-secrets-05-after.82181b3e.mp3",
      "afterAudioDurationSec": 4.205714,
      "afterTextHash": "82181b3ea65143d65b0155ce829eeefaf35f5718d13ca318d888cd1d4adc9363"
    },
    {
      "id": "tutorial-managing-secrets-06",
      "markerIndex": 5,
      "replayStartSec": 36.266224,
      "replayEndSec": 43.912931,
      "narrationText": "是时候证明密钥真的有效了。部署 repo。compose 文件同时使用了两种密钥：env 值通过插值注入，file 值通过 Docker secrets 挂载注入。",
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-managing-secrets/tutorial-managing-secrets-06.c291f475.mp3",
      "textHash": "c291f4754a2971b7593ba3eaab7d99941fafa34a270368849d09bf765caa854d",
      "audioDurationSec": 13.165714,
      "afterAudioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-managing-secrets/tutorial-managing-secrets-06-after.692eb9d4.mp3",
      "afterAudioDurationSec": 3.082449,
      "afterTextHash": "692eb9d4cbd7817c0646a7d3c49dd461b9e1385ccc0338a45ed8f92cb30de6c9"
    },
    {
      "id": "tutorial-managing-secrets-07",
      "markerIndex": 6,
      "replayStartSec": 43.912931,
      "replayEndSec": 51.957626,
      "narrationText": "env 密钥到达了吗？让容器打印该变量，值出现了：postgres.internal。应用确实收到了它。",
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-managing-secrets/tutorial-managing-secrets-07.5940532e.mp3",
      "textHash": "5940532eb7d34ac369a4ebcc94e3e183ccb0924f1566145fcbf44e25d00c9f87",
      "audioDurationSec": 9.325714,
      "afterAudioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-managing-secrets/tutorial-managing-secrets-07-after.44e21cd8.mp3",
      "afterAudioDurationSec": 3.317551,
      "afterTextHash": "44e21cd896d9537d435d38e1830fc5042bd82da0c67ce8a4ee758adbeb98d84e"
    },
    {
      "id": "tutorial-managing-secrets-08",
      "markerIndex": 7,
      "replayStartSec": 51.957626,
      "replayEndSec": 60.388557,
      "narrationText": "file 密钥呢？从容器内的 /run/secrets 读取。就在那里，是轮换后的值。应用能读取明文，只有工具拒绝向您显示。",
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-managing-secrets/tutorial-managing-secrets-08.f8fad1d3.mp3",
      "textHash": "f8fad1d302485eb8f472e151f83498ff85ec9fd150a51f0db402681b4fb0e05b",
      "audioDurationSec": 13.165714,
      "afterAudioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-managing-secrets/tutorial-managing-secrets-08-after.76c96cbe.mp3",
      "afterAudioDurationSec": 7.47102,
      "afterTextHash": "76c96cbe607137f45401d5c43d6e31aef1f3e8b55f403eaac1d324720d886bb0"
    },
    {
      "id": "tutorial-managing-secrets-09",
      "markerIndex": 8,
      "replayStartSec": 60.388557,
      "replayEndSec": 66.65807,
      "narrationText": "现在到了关键部分。我们将 fork 这个 repo。fork 是父级加密镜像的逐字节副本。",
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-managing-secrets/tutorial-managing-secrets-09.15cdab1f.mp3",
      "textHash": "15cdab1f2309f80e7c7676020bd494697ed8b39da8af909df7b766d948a35a74",
      "audioDurationSec": 7.079184,
      "afterAudioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-managing-secrets/tutorial-managing-secrets-09-after.aa3fa8cf.mp3",
      "afterAudioDurationSec": 4.04898,
      "afterTextHash": "aa3fa8cfda7b9eb92231188cd26404ab835147dab1b6a8a0b75abc25ceae0411"
    },
    {
      "id": "tutorial-managing-secrets-10",
      "markerIndex": 9,
      "replayStartSec": 66.65807,
      "replayEndSec": 71.050631,
      "narrationText": "但当我们列出 fork 的密钥时：空的。没有 Stripe 密钥，没有数据库密码，没有 API token。fork 无法冒充您。这就是「克隆生产环境、不破坏任何东西」真的有效的原因。",
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-managing-secrets/tutorial-managing-secrets-10.c82e78e4.mp3",
      "textHash": "c82e78e4c29b2f9f4a717b8e07dd517647f80a692d4f94fed4e98bf6928643c3",
      "audioDurationSec": 27.402449,
      "afterAudioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-managing-secrets/tutorial-managing-secrets-10-after.09dda45b.mp3",
      "afterAudioDurationSec": 4.284082,
      "afterTextHash": "09dda45b0a9b68dba13c6828ab7ff8943706023a326e770feb8d4800983fa141"
    },
    {
      "id": "tutorial-managing-secrets-11",
      "markerIndex": 10,
      "replayStartSec": 71.050631,
      "replayEndSec": 77.559823,
      "narrationText": "再来一个证明。尝试用父级 compose 启动 fork。失败了：Stripe 密钥的绑定源路径在 fork 下不存在。生产凭据永远不会随 fork 转移，即便是意外也不行。",
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-managing-secrets/tutorial-managing-secrets-11.50ae88f5.mp3",
      "textHash": "50ae88f53415890e164a3901a47d4c470b82fe11954026e2ccf34405225b7eab",
      "audioDurationSec": 15.229388,
      "afterAudioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-managing-secrets/tutorial-managing-secrets-11-after.0e447d50.mp3",
      "afterAudioDurationSec": 6.19102,
      "afterTextHash": "0e447d50ce4a1460c2a226a2d6cd99c371b40b43ff2d2769a3f3975b389bd7cb"
    }
  ],
  "narrationAudio": [
    {
      "id": "intro",
      "textHash": "bc25b0fa41dc932433aa85d17105b18b0643eca56f43a070be2170beb41717f4",
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-managing-secrets/intro.bc25b0fa.mp3",
      "narrationText": "是时候把真实凭据放到 fork 无法触及的地方了！我们将设置两个密钥，部署应用并证明它确实收到了它们，然后 fork 这个 repo，看着 fork 空手而归。它甚至无法启动。",
      "audioDurationSec": 15.490612
    },
    {
      "id": "env-trap",
      "textHash": "549d5e6b6e6a22bb3b7242ab0ba85ed7d50a59ac78c333ac5d42414f499470cd",
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-managing-secrets/env-trap.549d5e6b.mp3",
      "narrationText": "大多数团队会把 dotenv 文件放进 repo，因为这是最直接的做法。问题在于 fork 继承了镜像的逐字节副本，所以您的 sandbox 启动时会带着生产环境的 Stripe 密钥，并开始向真实客户收费。",
      "audioDurationSec": 18.755918
    },
    {
      "id": "write-only",
      "textHash": "f34abfbfcbc69e9e1940edcddecf9985a3d9da72a2d60f0049e2b831adcf6a2a",
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-managing-secrets/write-only.f34abfbf.mp3",
      "narrationText": "CLI 遵循 GitHub Actions 模型：get 返回摘要，而不是值本身。如果您忘记了密钥，不要试图查看，而是轮换它，审计日志会将其记录为蓄意更改。",
      "audioDurationSec": 16.039184
    },
    {
      "id": "fork-isolation",
      "textHash": "3fd3b9d7a9f1a728e64a00fd19235df08a57bcdddceb4e0d0ec665199dfde1b6",
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-managing-secrets/fork-isolation.3fd3b9d7.mp3",
      "narrationText": "这就是回报。fork 共享父级的加密数据，但密钥存储是按 repo 隔离的，所以 fork 的密钥列表为空，无法插值任何生产密钥，甚至无法启动父级的 compose。",
      "audioDurationSec": 17.475918
    },
    {
      "id": "next-tutorial",
      "textHash": "bba0aef101bd6819b530a3f6e24dd35c321c1df9270580b9687cc9c6a15f44f3",
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-managing-secrets/next-tutorial.bba0aef1.mp3",
      "narrationText": "这就是让 fork 无法触及的密钥锁定方案。下期见！",
      "audioDurationSec": 4.91102
    }
  ]
}
